国内非武汉地区本地新增病例首次实现零新增，局面完全可控。
The new cases in non-Wuhan area of China realized zero new cases for the first time.
韩国疫情得到初步控制；欧盟27国全部染疫；意大利扩大限流举措。
The South Korean outbreak was initially contained; all 27 EU countries were affected; and Italy expanded the containment initiative.
文 |《财经》数据研究员徐进 图 |《财经》视觉中心 编辑 | 郝洲一、国内形势盼巩固，境外输入局面可控今日国内简述：首先祝女士们节日快乐！特别要向战斗在“抗疫”一线的女士们致敬！国内3月7日报告新增病例44例。
Hsu Jin-tou, a data researcher with Caijing; editor and director of Caijing Visual Center. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
广大国内非武汉地区本地新增病例首次实现零新增。
For the first time, no new cases were recorded in non-Wuhan areas of China.
湖北非武汉地区连续三日零新增。
Hubei non-Wuhan area for three consecutive days added.
湖北棋看三招，已开始通过发放“绿码”方式着手有序恢复省内交通，为接下来有序推进全面复工复产做铺垫。
Hubei chess look at three moves, has started to issue "green code" approach to orderly restoration of traffic in the province, for the next orderly to promote the resumption of full-scale work.
武汉新增病例降至44例，“趋零”开始倒计时！北京、兰州口岸境外输入病例3例，分别来自意大利、西班牙和伊朗，均不涉及本地社区。
Wuhan dropped to 44 new cases, and the countdown to zero began! There were three imported cases from Italy, Spain and Iran outside the border ports of Beijing and Lanzhou, all of which did not involve local communities.
局面完全可控，应采取更积极姿态有序推进复工复产，恢复正常生活。
The situation can be completely controlled and a more active attitude should be adopted to promote the resumption of work and resume normal life.
二、全球疫情进入加速状态图1伊朗和意大利的疫情丝毫没有好转的迹象，单日新增均过千。
The Global Epidemic Entering Accelerated Status Chart 1 There are no signs of improvement in Iran and Italy, with more than a thousand new cases each day.
马耳他和保加利亚均首次报告病例，至此，欧盟27国无一幸免。
Malta and Bulgaria have reported cases for the first time, with no EU-27 country spared.
几个多日来无新增的国家再次出现新增案例，例如越南、柬埔寨、泰国、阿富汗、俄罗斯等。
New cases have re-emerged in countries that have not added more than a few days, such as Viet Nam, Cambodia, Thailand, Afghanistan and Russia.
图2为了避免让大家眼花缭乱，小编今天简化了此图，因政治地理关系将欧盟各国的数据累计展示在一条线里。
Fig. 2 To avoid dazzling everyone, the sketch is simplified today as the political geography of the countries of the European Union accumulated in a single line.
欧盟的新增确诊扶摇直上，达到1984例，看来势不可挡。
The number of new diagnoses in the European Union has soared to 1,984, which seems overwhelming.
这里需要特别指出的是：韩国图像的头部和右肩似已明确，预示疫情快速扩张的势头得到控制。
It should be noted that the head and right shoulder of the South Korean images seem to be clearly defined, indicating that the rapid spread of the epidemic is under control.
三、美国华府首报确诊病例，口罩库存只够1%需求图3美国单日新增破百，至3月7日，共有30个州出现确诊病例，首都华盛顿也报出首例感染。
2007-9-25 21: 36 Diagnosis is the first confirmed case in Washington, D.C., with only 1% of masks in stock. Chart 3 The United States broke new ground in one day.
纽约州州长科莫3月7日发表声明，宣布该州计入紧急状态。
The governor of New York state of emergency issued a statement March 7, declared a state of emergency.
为应对美国国内医疗物资紧缺的状况，特朗普政府已经对从中国进口的100多种医疗产品（包括口罩、净手湿巾、检查手套等）免除了进口关税，美国医疗系统一年需要的N95口罩数量约为3.5亿只，但目前美国只有需求量1%的库存。
In response to the shortage of medical supplies in the US, the Trump administration has exempted more than 100 medical products imported from China (including masks, clean hands wipes, gloves, etc.) from import duties, and the US health-care system needs about 350 million N95 million masks a year, but only about 1% of its current needs are in the US.
四、欧盟成员国全部染疫，意大利人口1/4限制流动图4不到一周时间，欧洲几乎无一幸免。
All member states of the European Union have been affected by the epidemic, and less than a quarter of Italy's population is confined to Figure 4.
马耳他和保加利亚昨日首次报告确诊病例。
Malta and Bulgaria reported confirmed cases for the first time yesterday.
图5意大利政府3月8日凌晨公布新法令，规定从3月8日起，除工作特殊原因及紧急状况，禁止出入伦巴第大区及分布在威尼托、艾米利亚-罗马涅、皮埃蒙特和马尔凯大区的14个省。
Fig. 5 The Italian Government issued a new decree in the early morning of 8 March prohibiting access to the Lombardy region and 14 provinces in the regions of Veneto, Emilia Romagna, Piedmont and Marquez, except for special reasons of work and emergencies.
伦巴第大区首府米兰及威尼托大区首府威尼斯都包括这一区域在内。
Both Milan, the capital of the Lombardy region, and Venice, the capital of the Veneto region, include this region.
法令规定在这些区域内包括大学和幼儿园在内的各级学校停课，暂停游行、宗教、葬礼等人员聚集活动。
The decree provides for the closure of schools at all levels, including universities and kindergartens, and the suspension of marches, religious services, funerals, etc., in these areas.
此外，法令规定，意大利全国范围内的游行、演出活动停止，迪厅、游戏厅、赌场等人员聚集场所也将全部关闭。
In addition, the decree stipulates that marches and performances throughout Italy will cease and that all places where people congregate, such as disco, game hall and casino, will be closed.
在酒吧及餐厅，也必须遵守保持人与人之间1米安全距离的规定。
In bars and restaurants, the 1 m safety distance between people must also be observed.
这一禁令将导致意大利全国1/4 人口被隔离，法令将持续到4月3日。
The ban, which will separate a quarter of Italy's population, will last until April 3.
五、韩国新增病例持续下降，60%感染病例与“新天地”教会相关图6韩国的确诊总数突破7000，新增病例持续下降，疫情有望得到控制。
New cases continue to decline in South Korea, 60% of infections and the church-related chart 6 South Korea has more than 7,000 confirmed cases, new cases continue to decline, the epidemic is expected to be brought under control.
在韩国政府的积极措施下，死亡率只有0.7%。
Thanks to the active measures of the Korean Government, the mortality rate is only 0.7 per cent.
韩国疾病管理本部长郑恩京指出，韩国72%的个案都是群聚感染，28.3%是零星个案，正在调查这些患者的感染来源。
In South Korea, 72 percent of cases are cluster infections and 28.3 percent are sporadic cases and the source of infection is being investigated, said Zheng Enjing, South Korea's minister for disease management.
此外，在全国所有个案中，60%与“新天地”教会有关。
In addition, 60 per cent of all cases in the country were related to the Church of New Horizons.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】六、全球疫情数字速览1、【世卫获2000万美元捐款】新华社3月8日称，中国政府决定向世卫（WHO）捐款2000万美元，作为推动国际合作抗疫。
The World Health Organization (WHO) has decided to donate 20 million US dollars to the World Health Organization (WHO) to promote international cooperation in the fight against the disease, Xinhua reported Wednesday.
中国响应世卫呼吁，支持其发挥专业优势，在全球抗疫发挥协调作用，特别是协助公共卫生较差的中小国家。
In response to the WHO call, China supports its professional advantages in playing a coordinating role in the global fight against the epidemic, especially in assisting small and medium-sized countries with poor public health.
2、【奥运或损失7.8万亿日元】日本三井住友证券公司估算，日本如果因新冠病毒取消举办东京夏季奥运会，可能会损失7.8万亿日元（约合743亿美元）。
Sumitomo Mitsui has estimated that Japan could lose 7.8 trillion yen ($74.3 billion) if it canceled the Tokyo Summer Games because of the new crown virus.
日本的GDP将下降1.4%。
Japan's GDP will fall by 1.4%.
此估算基于一种假设：如果到7月，新冠肺炎病毒疫情仍未正常化，就有可能取消奥运会。
The estimate is based on the assumption that the Olympics could be canceled if the outbreak of the new crown pneumonia virus is not normalized by July.
3、【硅谷12万名员工在家办公】疫情对美国的冲击越来越严重，苹果、脸书、微软、亚马逊、谷歌、推特等许多美国科技巨头也开始抗疫，纷纷要求自己的员工在家办公，远离硅谷和西雅图总部，总数约12万。
3, Silicon Valley 120,000 employees at home The impact of the epidemic on the United States is growing, with many U.S. technology giants such as Apple, Facebook, Microsoft, Amazon, Google and Twitter also fighting the epidemic, demanding that their employees work from home, away from Silicon Valley and Seattle headquarters, totaling about 120,000.
4、【60%农民工返岗】从国内各地监测的情况看，目前返岗复工的农民工达到7800万，占今年春节返乡的60%。
According to monitoring from all over the country, 78 million migrant workers have returned to work, accounting for 60 percent of the total.
从目前返岗复工的流向看，主要是长三角和珠三角。
From the current return to the flow of workers, mainly the Yangtze River Delta and the Pearl River Delta.
广东、浙江外省农民工返岗复工率达到70%，江苏外省农民工返岗复工率约60%。
The rate of migrant workers returning to work reached 70 percent in Guangdong and Zhejiang provinces, and about 60 percent in Jiangsu province.
目前农民工返程复工正有序进行。
At present migrant workers are returning to work in an orderly manner.
小结：国内非武汉地区本地新增病例首次实现零新增，武汉新增病例趋零进入倒计时，局面完全可控。
Summary: China's non-Wuhan region for the first time to achieve zero new cases, Wuhan to zero new cases into the countdown, the situation is fully controllable.
加快复工复产、恢复正常生活已成为当务之急。
Accelerating the resumption of work and rehabilitation has become an urgent task.
美国各州已经开始积极行动起来应对疫情，但白宫行动迟疑，仍未拉响警报。
States have begun to act aggressively to deal with the epidemic, but the White House has hesitated, but has yet to sound the alarm.
欧盟27国全部染疫。
All 27 EU countries have been infected.
意大利扩大“限流”举措。
Italy expands "current restraint" initiative.
